languages.text: "Отличная выдалась прогулка, {name}, не находишь? Только не зазнавайся, что вывел{mf||а} нас из тисков живого леса. Я бы и сам справился рано или поздно". {n}Винтерскейл усмехается и повторяет:{/n} "Рано или поздно".

traits.locale_text: "Отличная выдалась прогулка, {name}, не находишь? Только не зазнавайся, что вывел{mf||а} нас из тисков живого леса. Я бы и сам справился рано или поздно". {n}Винтерскейл усмехается и повторяет:{/n} "Рано или поздно".

languages.text: "A nice walk that, wasn't it, {name}? You may have helped us navigate the living forest's clutches, but don't let it go to your head. I would have managed by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats,{/n} "Sooner or later."

traits.locale_text: "A nice walk that was, wasn't it, {name}? Just don't let the fact that you had lead us out of the living forest's clutches go to your head. I would've managed to escape by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats:{/n} "Sooner or later."

languages.text: «Menudo paseíto, ¿verdad, {name}? Pero que no se le suba a la cabeza el habernos sacado de las garras de ese bosque viviente. Tarde o temprano habría escapado yo también». {n}Winterscale ríe entre dientes y repite:{/n} «Tarde o temprano».
languages.original_text: "A nice walk that, wasn't it, {name}? You may have helped us navigate the living forest's clutches, but don't let it go to your head. I would have managed by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats,{/n} "Sooner or later."

languages.text: “真是场不错的散步，是吧，{name}？或许你确实带着我们从森林里走了出来，但不要因此得意忘形，因为就算没有你，我也迟早能想办法走出去。”{n}温特斯凯尔笑了笑，重复道。{/n}“迟早。”
languages.original_text: "A nice walk that, wasn't it, {name}? You may have helped us navigate the living forest's clutches, but don't let it go to your head. I would have managed by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats,{/n} "Sooner or later."

traits.locale_text: “真是场不错的散步，是吧，{name}？你带领我们脱离了森林的魔爪。不过，不要因此得意忘形，因为就算没有你，我也迟早能想办法走出去。”{n}温特斯凯尔笑了笑，重复道。{/n}“迟早。”

languages.text: « C'était une belle balade, n'est-ce pas, {name} ? Mais ne prenez pas la grosse tête simplement parce que vous nous avez sortis des griffes de cette maudite forêt. J'aurais réussi à m'extirper de cet enfer tout seul tôt ou tard... tôt ou tard, » {n}ajoute-t-il en poussant un petit rire.{/n}
languages.original_text: "A nice walk that, wasn't it, {name}? You may have helped us navigate the living forest's clutches, but don't let it go to your head. I would have managed by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats,{/n} "Sooner or later."

languages.text: 「いい散歩だったな、{name}？お前は俺たちを生きている森の魔手から連れ出してくれたが、調子に乗るなよ。遅かれ早かれ、俺一人で脱出できただろうがな」{n}ウィンタースケールは笑いながら繰り返す。{/n}「遅かれ早かれ、な」
languages.original_text: "A nice walk that, wasn't it, {name}? You may have helped us navigate the living forest's clutches, but don't let it go to your head. I would have managed by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats,{/n} "Sooner or later."

traits.locale_text: 「いい散歩だったな、{name}？ただ、お前が俺たちを生きている森の魔手から連れ出してくれたという事実を、頭から消し去ってはいけない。遅かれ早かれ、俺一人で脱出できただろうがな」{n}ウィンタースケールは笑いながら繰り返す。{/n}「遅かれ早かれ、な」

languages.text: "Das war ein schöner Spaziergang, nicht wahr, {name}? Ihr habt uns vielleicht geholfen, den Fängen des lebenden Waldes zu entkommen, aber lasst Euch das nicht zu Kopf steigen. Das wäre mir früher oder später auch alleine gelungen." {n}Winterzunder lacht und wiederholt:{/n} "Früher oder später."
languages.original_text: "A nice walk that, wasn't it, {name}? You may have helped us navigate the living forest's clutches, but don't let it go to your head. I would have managed by myself sooner or later." {n}Winterscale chuckles and repeats,{/n} "Sooner or later."

traits.locale_text: "Das war ein schöner Spaziergang, nicht wahr, {name}? Lasst Euch aber nicht die Tatsache zu Kopf steigen, dass Ihr uns aus den Klauen des lebenden Waldes geführt habt. Ich wäre auch alleine früher oder später entkommen." {n}Winterzunder lacht und wiederholt:{/n} "Früher oder später."
